      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 500,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "text": "Write savings: 4 bytes written per backedge vs 3084 bytes. ~771x less per edge!",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-02T21:04:22.135Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-02T21:04:22.135Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnhyqa9ezg0po6gjsc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 522,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "text": "With compaction amortized over 25 backedges: 3084/25 = 123 bytes avg — still 25x less",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-02T21:04:22.135Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-02T21:04:22.135Z",
